ur C. Clarke Award (The Children of Time Novels)","description":"From the award-winning master of sci-fi Adrian Tchaikovsky, Children of Memory is the unmissable follow-up space opera to the highly acclaimed Children of Time and Children of Ruin.\n\nThey dreamed of a new home.\nThey woke to a nightmare.\n\nOn Imir, Captain Holt founded a new colony on an empty world. In the process, he created hope and a new future for humanity. But, generations later, his descendan\u2026","authors":["Adrian Tchaikovsky"],"imageUrl":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51jsO1+QriL.jpg","hasSample":false,"amazonRating":4.300000190734863,"numberOfReviews":7719},"customerProfile":{"class":"customerProfile","penName":"Tarjei Utnes","realName":"Tarjei Utnes"},"authorBiosBSE":{"class":"authorBioList","authors":[{"class":"authorBio","asin":"B002XLHS8Q","name":"Adrian Tchaikovsky","bio":"Adrian Tchaikovsky was born in Woodhall Spa, Lincolnshire before heading off to Reading to study psychology and zoology. For reasons unclear even to himself he subsequently ended up in law and has worked as a legal executive in both Reading and Leeds, where he now lives. Married, he is a keen live role-player and occasional amateur actor, has trained in stage-fighting, and keeps no exotic or dangerous pets of any kind, possibly excepting his son. Catch up with Adrian at www.shadowsoftheapt.com for further information about both himself and the insect-kinden, together with bonus material including short stories and artwork. Author Website: http://shadowsoftheapt.com/","imageUrl":"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61Y3AAn6fSL.jpg"}]},"currentBook":{"class":"featuredRecommendation","asin":"B07KPMJ7V9","title":"Children of Ruin (The Children of Time Novels)","description":"'Asimov or Clarke might have written this' \u2013 Stephen Baxter, co-author of The Long Earth\n\nA scout ship discovers a human outpost lying derelict in space \u2013 and a planet better left unexplored. Set in the same universe as Children of Time, this is a thrilling narrative from the award-winning Adrian Tchaikovsky.\n\nIt has been waiting through the ages. Now it's time . . .\n\nThousands of years ago, Earth\u2026","authors":["Adrian Tchaikovsky"],"imageUrl":"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51K8H9HxPeL.jpg","hasSample":false,"amazonRating":4.300000190734863,"numberOfReviews":14944},"authorBios":{"class":"authorBioList","authors":[{"class":"authorBio","asin":"B002XLHS8Q","name":"Adrian Tchaikovsky","bio":"Adrian Tchaikovsky was born in Woodhall Spa, Lincolnshire before heading off to Reading to study psychology and zoology. For reasons unclear even to himself he subsequently ended up in law and has worked as a legal executive in both Reading and Leeds, where he now lives. Married, he is a keen live role-player and occasional amateur actor, has trained in stage-fighting, and keeps no exotic or dangerous pets of any kind, possibly excepting his son. Catch up with Adrian at www.shadowsoftheapt.com for further information about both himself and the insect-kinden, together with bonus material including short stories and artwork. Author Website: http://shadowsoftheapt.com/","imageUrl":"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61Y3AAn6fSL.jpg"}]},"authorSubscriptions":{"class":"authorSubscriptionInfoList","subscriptions":[{"class":"authorSubscriptionInfo","asin":"B002XLHS8Q","name":"Adrian Tchaikovsky","subscribed":false,"imageUrl":"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61Y3AAn6fSL.jpg"}]}},"bottomSheetEnabled":true}